  <!-- 高能水栽培 -->
  <ResearchProjectDef ParentName="AdvancedWanjietechBase">
    <defName>WanjietechHighEnergyHydroponicsBasin</defName>
    <label>High-energy Hydroponics Basin</label>
    <description>With the development of Wanjietech, your demand for high-energy fruits is growing.
      Studying this unique cultivation method can greatly speed up the ripening of high-energy
      fruits, but this cultivation method cannot be applied to other common plants.</description>
